### Welcome to appbase-redis

### `v0.1` - Brave Souls

```
$ git clone https://github.com/appbaseio/appbase-redis.git
$ npm install
$ npm test
$ node index.js // starts a http server
```

### Authors and Contributors
@sacheendra and @siddharthlatest

### Support or Contact
File issues here - https://github.com/appbaseio/appbase-redis/issues.
